      "para_id": "Q001854.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Ibbi-Suen , the king of his land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Aḫam-arši , the scribe , child of Babati , is your servant ."
    }
